title: Book I Found
author: Killapiez5
pages:
#- "Wake Up!" is the cry of rabble-rousers everywhere. Trouble is, people are generally content to slumber on; after all, waking up sucks. Sleeping can be pretty comfotable. Some things, though, are so jarring, so loud, so tremendous that they jar people 
#- from sleep forcefully, throwing them unceremoniously into conciousness. Thunder is one of those things, the tremendous boom that comes with the spark of lightning. Lightning flashes forth from the sky, striking the ground, setting the world aflame.
#- And then the thunder shakes the sleepers from their beds, waking them to the fire that rages.
#- 